    <body>
        <div xml:id="NA387-kiḷavi">
            <p type="edition">itu piriviṭai melinta talaimakaḷait tōḻi paruvaṅ kāṭṭi vaṟpuṟīiyatu (EV: vaṟpuṟuttiyatu).</p>
            <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante encouraged HER, who had become weak in the time of separation, by pointing out the season.</p>
            </div>
      <div xml:id="NA387">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            neṟiyiruṅ katuppu nīṇṭa tōḷu</l>
<l>            mamma nāḷun toṉṉalañ citaiya</l>
<l>            vōrāc centoṭai yorīiya kaṇṇik</l>
<l>            kallā maṟavar villiṭai vilaṅkiya</l>
<l>            tuṉṉaruṅ kavalai yaruñcura miṟantōr</l>
<l>            varuvar vāḻi tōḻi ceruviṟan</l>
<l>            tālaṅ kāṉat tañcuvara viṟutta</l>
<l>            vēlkeḻu tāṉaic ceḻiyaṉ pācaṟai</l>
<l>            yuṟaikaḻi vāḷiṉ miṉṉi yutukkā</l>
<l>            ṇeṭumperuṅ kuṉṟa muṟṟik</l>
<l>            kaṭumpeyal poḻiyuṅ kalikeḻu vāṉē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent">            The curly dark hair and the long shoulders,</l>
<l rend="indent">            alas, while [their] old beauty is wasted daily,</l>
<l>        will he come, oh friend,</l>
<l>        he who traversed the difficult desert with crossroads difficult to approach,</l>
<l rend="indent">            obstructed in between by the bows of the untaught bold ones</l>
<l rend="indent2">            with chaplets, who regardless abandoned straight arrows?</l>
<l rend="indent">            Flashing like a sword drawn from the sheath</l>
<l rend="indent2">            in the encampment of Ceḻiyaṉ with an army full of spears</l>
<l rend="indent3">            that tarried for fear to come to the banyan forest<note place="foot">Or <term xml:lang="ta">Ālaṅkāṉam</term> can be read as the name of a place.</note>, crossing a conflict,</l>
<l rend="indent4">            see there:</l>
<l rend="indent">            the bustling sky that flows with fierce rain,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            after ripening in the long big hills.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
